OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBasildon Hospital patient's
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwedding ring stolen on     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FChristmas Day              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man's wedding ring was stolen while  
OL,6, he was in hospital on Christmas Day.   
OL,8,FThe man, who is in his 70s, was        
OL,9,Freceiving treatment at Basildon        
OL,10,FHospital when the theft took place,    
OL,11,FEssex Police said.                     
OL,13,FThe force said the wedding ring was    
OL,14,Ftaken from the patient at about 15:00  
OL,15,FGMT.                                   
OL,17,FThe force has appealed for anyone who  
OL,18,Frecognises the ring or who believes    
OL,19,Fthey may have been offered it for sale 
OL,20,Fto contact officers.                   
